Pleasant most of the time– tho. squalls of snow frequnt– I
                    did not go to Chh. after a rest + nap – walked 30
                    min&sdotlow;

Pleasant – Saw Dr Prince for final visit
                    – gav up Baths to go home next Wed.
                        12&th;

A rainy day so tht I did not walk all day – It pour&ddotlow; down
                    at time– Toward Eve it look&ddotlow;
                    like clearing but fail&ddotlow; to do So–
